{"type": "article", "id": 7351, "title": "Nike 跑鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-13T07:22:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135213IEFxrgu0U2esS6Bf.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这个系列的跑鞋是 Nike 前几天送给全世界女人的妇女节礼物，这 6 款跑鞋分别以东京，纽约，伦敦，巴黎，米兰和上海这 6 个世界大都市为灵感来源，设计了不同的印花，如纽约的玫瑰，巴黎的百合，上海的梅花。整个系列浪漫灵动，似乎把整个春天都穿到了身上。这一系列已经在 3 月 8 日全面上线，<a href=\"http://www.nike.com/cn/zh_cn/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以买到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135209AVWQYCtpqmku2wTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53468208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135210aqxoPB5HG4ULkrf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135210aN43rc58iqQoBCSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135211IZPS60Usy3NibHBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135211zbGhBqiDoj4NWOPZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src